{"id": 1302, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x荣耀】你在什么情况下会觉得你的手机特别不争气？", "description": "有时候也是忍不住想温柔地把它扔在地上训斥它。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 7227, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161103101052JhD5OFvB3dciwmbk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-04T03:00:49Z", "options": [{"id": 137216, "content": "自拍太模糊.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847601}, {"id": 130304, "content": "一直转圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814544}, {"id": 133633, "content": "收不到喜欢的人信息了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832207}, {"id": 130306, "content": "你要扫一扫，它要等一等。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820622}, {"id": 130562, "content": "看电视看到最精彩的地方，然后，缓冲，", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821560}, {"id": 130307, "content": "超市买东西，打开支付宝的时候慢如狗，后面排队的小哥小妹都盯着你手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820492}, {"id": 130565, "content": "明明看着很美的风景，但是它就是拍不出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821562}, {"id": 130312, "content": "还有20%电量，却自动关机了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738170}, {"id": 135178, "content": "屏幕太大，边边角角的单手够不到。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651741}, {"id": 130315, "content": "经不起摔，然后破费。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 661117}, {"id": 134668, "content": "荣耀这款机器就不争气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568460}, {"id": 130316, "content": "没信号？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686426}, {"id": 130572, "content": "思维赶不及算了，还赶不上我手指速度的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814709}, {"id": 131085, "content": "朋友站在旁边，手机这时候卡成狗的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820967}, {"id": 131853, "content": "发发卡包", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825096}, {"id": 134157, "content": "玩游戏正激烈突然卡顿卡的要死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834442}, {"id": 130317, "content": "组队联赛，关键时刻卡了，辣鸡！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810532}, {"id": 130573, "content": "網慢，當機", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786848}, {"id": 131598, "content": "被偷的时候，怎么不喊呢！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679729}, {"id": 130318, "content": "满是指纹，满是指纹，防指纹膜都没用", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727381}, {"id": 130574, "content": "想下游戏结果闪退的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821565}, {"id": 130319, "content": "没电。卡到死机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820631}, {"id": 130575, "content": "连不WiFi", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812781}, {"id": 131088, "content": "用了一会就没电……好捉急", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 823159}, {"id": 130320, "content": "Hey Siri！喊了一百遍也不理我", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508750}, {"id": 130576, "content": "关键时刻，卡死！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821593}, {"id": 130832, "content": "转眼之间，人还在，电没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721454}, {"id": 136977, "content": "在紧急时刻卡卡卡卡成狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846770}, {"id": 130322, "content": "Hey Siri！喊一百遍也不搭理我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508750}, {"id": 131859, "content": "联不上无线网", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824857}, {"id": 132883, "content": "看大尺度图片的时候，人家把头凑过来，关不及。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293643}, {"id": 149011, "content": "玩的正嗨的时候显示低电量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 884570}, {"id": 130579, "content": "iPhone还不如人家千元机分辨率高", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770819}, {"id": 132884, "content": "想偷拍个美女，当相机打开的时候只留下她体香", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293643}, {"id": 143892, "content": "之前干什么都好好的 突然要玩游戏了或者回复消息了它瞬间关机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867018}, {"id": 130326, "content": "WP用户，争气是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663461}, {"id": 130584, "content": "想上Twitter和Ins的时候，想起来还要翻墙。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821611}, {"id": 130585, "content": "不想戴套，但是怕摔！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821624}, {"id": 131354, "content": "一上火车就没信号", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824087}, {"id": 131870, "content": "其实我想说你们忘了华为专门什么的吗\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592415}, {"id": 130590, "content": "不管储存空间还剩多少都会显示“手机储存空间不足”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796159}, {"id": 130592, "content": "每次苹果有新功能，都被说是安卓玩剩下的时…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287134}, {"id": 130593, "content": "随着大数据时代，广告变的无孔不入……搜索过什么，给你看什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 520248}, {"id": 130849, "content": "没网，没信号，没电", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803853}, {"id": 130594, "content": "喜欢的人好不容易回消息了活着和喜欢的人正聊的火热的时候手机关机了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821653}, {"id": 131108, "content": "相机自带美颜效果把人拍的更丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784712}, {"id": 130596, "content": "工厂阿迪直销➕WX：ace2375", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821642}, {"id": 130597, "content": "死机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632374}, {"id": 130598, "content": "没内存", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632374}, {"id": 149799, "content": "难道不是南方的弱机一到北方就自己被冻关机？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887288}]}